(1/100) Hey, I’m @urja_sardesai — and today marks the beginning of a journey that’s deeply personal to me. 🥹💖

For the next 100 days, I’m challenging myself to show up every single day — with content that’s honest, intentional, and unapologetically me.✨❣️

This journey will take me right up to my 23rd birthday, and my biggest hope? 25K FOLLOWERS!!!! 🥰That I’ll grow into someone who embraces consistency, nurtures a community filled with love, and learn to balance both my PG life and creative passion — without letting either slip through the cracks.🥳❤️‍🔥

It won’t be easy, but it will be real. And I’m so glad to have you with me for it. Join me 💌
